text: CFRN may refer to: * CFRN (AM), a radio station (1260 AM) licensed to serve Edmonton, Alberta, Canada * CFRN-DT, a television station (channel 3) licensed to serve Edmonton * CFBR-FM, a radio station (100.3 FM) licensed to serve Edmonton, which held the call sign CFRN-FM from 1951 to 1979 * Certified Flight Registered Nurse * Coalition for Rainforest Nations
title: CFRN
